title: S16 Ep102: Close Encounters of the 5th Kind w/ Martin Keller
itunes:title: Close Encounters of the 5th Kind w/ Martin Keller
description:
Darkness Radio presents Close Encounters of the 5th Kind with Martin Keller

Dave & Tim return to the skies with guest Martin Keller as he shares tales of Close Encounters of the 5th Kind — human-initiated contact — in unusual geographical locations to high strangeness episodes at his home. 

Get the book here: https://amzn.to/2WfcZEP

See his website here:  thespacepenclub.com/
